From coburnn Nicholas Coburn Subject Re Shipping a bike In article Manish Vij writes Can someone recommend how to ship a motorcycle from San Francisco to Seattle And how much might it cost I remember a thread on If someone saved the instructions on bike prep please post 'em again or Thanks Manish Step Join the AMA American Motorcycling Association Call AMA Step After you become a member they will ship your bike UNCRATED to just about anywhere across the fruited plain for a few hundred I have used this service and have been continually They usually only take a few days for the whole thing and you do not have to prepare the bike in any way other than draining the gas Not to mention that it is about of the normal shipping costs by the time you crate a bike and ship it with another company you can pay around Nick Coburn DoD AMA ' '